NAME
    Module::LocalLoad - Load modules from local env

SYNOPSIS
      my $module = 'IO::File';
      load($module) and printf("%s v%s loaded\n", $module, $module->VERSION);

DESCRIPTION
    Let your global modules be locals, and place them in a safe haven where
    no one but you can, and will, hurt them.

ENVIRONMENT
    PERL5HACKLIB

